Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to see if you'd like to get some\Ntea and talk about Mr. Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm in a bit of a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a meeting my dad needs to chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,About the upcoming dance party...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.46,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(360,340)}Sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably has nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have I seen her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really my taste, but my friend made me buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I can't tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a state congress dinner meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just an ordinary dinner meeting either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll have no problem finding\Na date for the dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really want to go anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you looking up info on Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to hide it. I'm investigating her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for a college report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cultural anthropology major, Lotte Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite impressive, Ms. Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about the accountant murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a newspaper article about\Nthe "Voice of God" murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is about the murders of the middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confidence in my ability to gather information,\Nbut you definitely beat me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking into all the unsolved murders\Nin the Bayern area in the last 4 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me everything you know about the\Nmurder of Margot Langer, the ex-prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of Margot Langer and Hans Schuwald was\Njoyously reunited with Mr. Schuwald, the millionaire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and has become his successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a possibility that the son is involved\Nin the incidents surrounding Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm 100% sure he's not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in this pretty deep for just a college report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't for a research paper at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does a person like you even have anything to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything goes just how you want when\Nyou're as pretty as you are, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably have no love problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't bother you with my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,God is so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hang out with me\Ntonight? There's a dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really used to places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that. If I'm with\Nyou, everyone will talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See look. Everyone's looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take your leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See! Here's one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Constantine from the Supernatural Phenomenon\NResearch Group. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, a weird one has come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe a guy like him has\Nthe balls to approach you, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be my dance partner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave together, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we fit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tons of guys have come up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been cold to every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been so long since I've had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All the students are gathered here and having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really been a long time since I've\Nbeen around something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just very different than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lotte. I begging you, dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here again! He's a persistent little bugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a while. C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's drunk this time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? You're so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! One dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get my money then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Money? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop asking questions. Karl asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to be your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just dance with me a little bit. That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for one song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! I'm sorry! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped him search for his father because I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we proved that he was Schuwald's real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have things to do with my dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"I promised my dad that..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dad this. Dad that."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought being ignored would be this painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It does hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It all hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad things can't continue to happen forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where I can get in contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don't have a place to live yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then call me at home. Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find who you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have sworn I've seen her somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks just like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's probably due to the accuracy\Nof the gun rather than your aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It failed the trials for the German Army, but it will\Nhit within 5 cm of where you aim from 300 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're going to shoot, but\Nas you get closer, the accuracy increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing after that is picking a spot\Nwhere nothing will get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets are .338 Lapua Magnums.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It can hold four bullets, but you won't\Nhave time to shoot all four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end for you, if you can't do it in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bird watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of visitors every week on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man and those two young ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm apologizing to this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been for over sixty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this? He just left that\Nfood that we're so famous for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, answer the quiz and win some wonderful prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first contestant is Mr. Weindler from Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an... RV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what my family always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Weindler seems excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great if his family could go camping with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But he needs to get ten questions right\Nor he doesn't leave with the RV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Question number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to go home without\Ntouching your food again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You came a week ago. I remember every customer's\Nface, no matter how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not hungry, at least take the soup home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You look horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to shoot him in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I lost my footing after walking\Nin this forest for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anything is broken. I performed first aid,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but please have it looked at in a hospital as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw you I thought you were\Na hunter, but it seems that you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds are gathering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, there was a man. The wild\Nbirds would ride on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If he held out his hand like this\Nthe birds would land on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was a child, he would always spend\Ntime with the birds in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then came the age of Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He belonged to the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly believed that the National Socialist German Workers' Party
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,would bring prosperity to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, he received some orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A vicious criminal was hiding out in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he knew the forest so well, he\Nwas sent to chase after the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was ordered to find the criminal and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He chased and chased the criminal through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When he caught him, the man he chased wasn't a criminal at all. He was just an ordinary foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no way of knowing beforehand\Nwho this person really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he simply carried out his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, the birds have never\Nridden on his shoulders ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For over sixty years, he has been apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the birds never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will blood flow through this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}A Child's View
